            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間12日03:09，恆生科技指數下跌179.09點（或3%），暫報5788.14點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+7.8%</li><li>近 1 月：+16.04%</li><li>近 3 月：+31.68%</li><li>近 6 月：+72.92%</li><li>今年以來：+33.55%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>賭場及博彩概念領跌-3.68%。其中    中國生態旅遊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01371:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01371\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01371-HK</a>)            下跌        32.35%            ;        匯彩控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01180:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01180\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01180-HK</a>)            下跌        8.47%            ;        NIRAKU(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01245:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01245\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01245-HK</a>)            下跌        6.4%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大中華區概念領跌-2.66%。其中    ＸＬ二南方恒科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:07226:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/07226\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">07226-HK</a>)            下跌        5.18%            ;        ＦＬ二南方國指(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:07288:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/07288\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">07288-HK</a>)            下跌        2.71%            ;        ＦＬ二南方恒指(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:07200:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/07200\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">07200-HK</a>)            下跌        2.43%    。</p></section></main>",
